{"tid":987372,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[有感而發]咁就一年了","createTime":"2019-01-19T09:10:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-19T14:10:08.000Z","uid":36961,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7c5585b3577db405d870f6a66451a1b52c67cf41","tid":987372,"uid":36961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T09:10:18.000Z","msg":"每年呢個時候 都會手多執間房<br />\n明明知 執完可能都仲係咁亂<br />\n但都想做番次掃除<br />\n點知睇番啲野 先知道 哦原來時間過得咁快<br />\n小學個本紀念冊 中學同學寫既聖誕卡<br />\nOcamp啲人寫既龜背<br />\n你第一個女朋友送比你既禮物 你第一次整禮物比人整剩既既材料 傷得你最深既人 你傷得最深既人<br />\n一啲已經唔存在唔再同你人生有交集既人同埋事<br />\n雖然係咁 但係你都好唔捨得咁將佢地扔左佢<br />\n永遠都留番一個位擺呢堆野 明知呢啲野係有幾無用 你都唔會扔佢<br />\n可能直到有一日 你會扔走佢地 但唔係依一刻<br />\n因為 你仲未放低到呢啲記憶 或者係自己念舊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 各位農曆新年快樂"},{"pid":"1a5d67b4faaa114ba4df46a5b7c704130785cdd2","tid":987372,"uid":135035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T09:10:47.000Z","msg":"Copy cat<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85f07a8262d517740b9737522551f6fa4ed576de","tid":987372,"uid":179867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T09:11:52.000Z","msg":"年經？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e73c0868463b8ce648977e83061538f1beeb4013","tid":987372,"uid":55458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a5d67b4faaa114ba4df46a5b7c704130785cdd2","tid":987372,"uid":135035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T09:10:47.000Z","msg":"Copy cat<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T09:13:08.000Z","msg":"複製貓？"},{"pid":"f36d4a5c72ebced6432b9d223c65600ae7bbed8d","tid":987372,"uid":36961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a5d67b4faaa114ba4df46a5b7c704130785cdd2","tid":987372,"uid":135035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T09:10:47.000Z","msg":"Copy cat<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" cla